text: The Saint Afram Syriac Orthodox Cathedral is a Syriac Orthodox cathedral in Södertälje in Sweden. It was opened in 1983, and is governed by the Syriac Orthodox Patriarchate's Representation in Sweden. ==References== ==Other websites== *http://www.stafrem.se/page.php?p=16 official website Category:Cathedrals in Sweden Category:1983 establishments in Sweden
title: Saint Afram Syriac Orthodox Cathedral
